    },
    {
      "id": "guard-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 2100,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "Never fabricates — if no source confirms it, SAGE doesn't say it\n\nHedges when uncertain — strong evidence stated as fact, weak evidence flagged\n\nSources on every answer — every claim references where it was found\n\nEscalation awareness — flags when something is out of CSM scope\n\nSource hierarchy — when sources conflict, internal reality overrides official docs\n\nConversation isolation — no assumptions bleed between customers",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "baseline": 18,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 42,
      "version": 1,
